FBIS3-1939 "drchi042_k_94022" FBIS-CHI-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Li Lanqing Speaks on Educational Reform, Development OW0203142694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1355 GMT 2 Mar 94 OW0203142694 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 2 (XINHUA) -- Vice-Premier Li Lanqing today spoke to a meeting of 800 teachers and students held at the People's University of China on current affairs and government policy. Those present came from all the universities in Beijing. On educational reform and development, Li noted that China will further promote the development of scientific, technological and educational services to accelerate modernization.
